Title: Metro Launch
Description: Metro Launch is a new Start menu inspired by Windows 8's.
HomeWiki:
Metro Launch is a new Start menu written in AutoIt v3, inspired by Windows 8's.

Features:
  • Customizable Lock screen
  • Tiles
  • Pure Metro UI style
  • You can pin files and executables

Requisites:
  • Windows 7, Windows Vista or Windows XP
